node.text:
have you ever woke up from a dream and instantly has the urge to jump right back into it? to go back into the adventure wherever you were exploring? this is a part of discovering your true passions and living them. experiencing something that once seemed like a dream but is now a part of your journey. live a life guided by what makes you smile, excited, and curious. what your passions are, what your dreams are, can all be accomplished. it’s as simple as envisioning yourself doing it. ✨
.
this amazing edit by @gastongardey encompasses just that. that feeling of exploring your actual dreams, turning every one of your minds creations into actual experience. @gastongardey has been a part of this nature backs family for years and we’re beyond grateful for the work and inspiration you bring us daily. this is truly inspiring and it just shows that every dream you have is a new adventure waiting for you to discover it 🌎
.
nature backs - experience the moment.

node.text: After an amazing time at one of the biggest outdoor events in the country (Outdoor Retailer) the NB squad found their way to the mountains. Now it was time to really have some fun, hit the slopes, cook big meals and let our minds wander into the winter night sky. We stayed in a beautiful cabin in Winter Park, which is a little over an hour outside of Denver, and truly let the vibes roll. Come get a mini look at how our Winter Park experience went! As always, much love fam. Till next time!

node.text:
🌿new shirt, new chapter 🌿
- we’re beyond excited to introduce our first 100% organic shirt to you! this is such an amazing community, and as we grow we’re aware of the impact and energy we create. this is why we’re beginning the next step in our journey to create products that are more friendly and sustainable for our earth.
.
we’ve worked over a year to make the perfect fit, feel, and experience that you love with these shirts. we’ve partnered with a fair trade certified manufacturer to create this super soft 100% organic shirt made with eco friendly fibers, less water, and less energy.
.
our new Woven shirts are inspired by the stories of our lives and how their connected to our natural spaces. we are interwoven with the plants, moon, the trees, the sands, to each other and everything in between. the Woven reminds us how our actions and beliefs interact with the All. the intentions we set and the threads we weave can bring us to a place of serenity and harmony. be there with the Woven.
.
join us on this next chapter and continue inspiring all to experience the moment and embrace the beauty of nature. hit us up with any questions or ideas you have for how to continue this journey. we’re incredibly grateful for your support and for being a part of this community. we couldn’t do this without your energy and love, all the warmth to you!
.
all the love to @rayco.design for creating the beautiful art for this shirt. we’re constantly inspired by her creativity and passion.🌍
.
big shout out and much love to @emileephelps for capturing these shots and helping us move into this new chapter ☀️
.

node.text:
van life anyone? 🏞
- absolutely loving all the inspiration coming from one of our content creators @roamingwithriley_ while out on the road in his nature backs adventure van. its something that many of us have dreamt of, to live out of a vehicle and travel to all the adventures around. it’s awesome to see riley doing it and bringing us all the vibes.
.
what’s special about living on the road are the endless opportunities to experience. the freedom to explore not only our earth, but yourself. being on the road and in nature eliminates the constant distractions that we encounter on our daily lives. you become more aware that our earth offers all you need. it brings you to peace, it calms your mind, and reveals a world of comfort and accessibility. 
.
what’s beautiful is that you don’t HAVE to live in a vehicle and travel around to experience this. you can experience it now, be it on a walk through the woods, a weekend trip, or a night out under the stars, you can always feel the freedom nature brings us. embrace this state of being, live within it.
.
all the love to @roamingwithriley_ with the inspiration and beauty.
.

WINNER/PRIZES: 
We will select 3 RANDOM winners to win 1st, 2nd, and 3rd place prizes of the following:

1st: 
	⁃	$300 AirBnB Gift Card
	⁃	$300 donation to a non-profit in your name to help with a cause you’re passionate about

2nd:

Aside from the 3 major winners, we will randomly select 25 of y’all to win something sweet, so keep your eyes peeled 👀

WINNERS WILL BE ANNOUNCED THIS THURSDAY 🤘🏼

HOW TO ENTER:
- Tag a friend in the comments (1 Tagged friend = 1 Entry, Multiple entries encouraged)
- Be following us

BONUS ENTRIES
-Screenshot and repost the giveaway to you stories (must tag us)
-Comment what non-profit you’d donate to
-Reply to someone's comment (meet someone new)

We recognize that not everyone has the ability to donate to something they support, but we know everyone has something they care for. So, along with the nb gear and air bnb gift card, we’re spreading the love and support! Share who you’d wanna give to with your comment, this is a great way for us to learn about other non profits/issues that are important to this community. Much love to every single one of you, this community continues to inspire us daily. This is just the beginning! 🤘🏼🌎
.
BE AWARE OF ANY FAKE ACCOUNTS TRYING TO IMPERSONATE US!! We only have ONE account and it’s this one (@naturebacks) which we’ll be directly reaching out to the winners from. Thank you!!
